<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Drift | Gentle Habit Building</title>
    <script>
        (() => {
            const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem("drift-theme");
            const systemPrefersDark = window.matchMedia("(prefers-color-scheme: dark)").matches;
            const theme = savedTheme || (systemPrefersDark ? "dark" : "light");
            document.documentElement.setAttribute("data-theme", theme);
        })();
    </script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page-shell">
        <header class="site-header">
            <a href="/" class="brand">Daily Reminder</a>
            <div class="header-controls">
                <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Primary">
                    <a href="#features">Why it works</a>
                    <a href="#rhythm">Daily rhythm</a>
                    <a href="#support">Support</a>
                    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                </nav>
                <button type="button" class="theme-toggle" data-theme-toggle aria-label="Switch color theme">
                    <span class="theme-toggle-label">Dark mode</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main>
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="hero-copy">
                    <p class="eyebrow">Small routines. Real momentum.</p>
                    <h1>Build habits that fit quietly into everyday life.</h1>
                    <p class="hero-text">
                        Drift helps you stay consistent with a few meaningful habits at a time.
                        No streak pressure, no crowded dashboards, just a calm space to return to each day.
                    </p>
                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="/dashboard" class="button button-primary">Open your routine</a>
                        <a href="#features" class="button button-secondary">See how it feels</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-card" aria-label="Habit preview">
                    <div class="hero-card-top">
                        <p>Today&rsquo;s rhythm</p>
                        <span>3 gentle wins</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="habit-list">
                        <article class="habit-item habit-item-complete">
                            <div>
                                <p class="habit-title">Drink water before coffee</p>
                                <p class="habit-note">A soft start for the morning</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="habit-status">Done</span>
                        </article>

                        <article class="habit-item">
                            <div>
                                <p class="habit-title">10 minute walk</p>
                                <p class="habit-note">Move a little after lunch</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="habit-status">Next</span>
                        </article>

                        <article class="habit-item">
                            <div>
                                <p class="habit-title">Write one line in journal</p>
                                <p class="habit-note">End the day with reflection</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="habit-status">Later</span>
                        </article>
                    </div>

                    <div class="progress-panel">
                        <div>
                            <p class="progress-label">This week</p>
                            <p class="progress-value">5 calm check-ins</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-dots" aria-hidden="true">
                            <span class="dot dot-filled"></span>
                            <span class="dot dot-filled"></span>
                            <span class="dot dot-filled"></span>
                            <span class="dot"></span>
                            <span class="dot"></span>
                            <span class="dot"></span>
                            <span class="dot"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="feature-strip" id="features">
                <article>
                    <p class="feature-kicker">Focused</p>
                    <h2>Track only the habits that matter right now.</h2>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <p class="feature-kicker">Encouraging</p>
                    <h2>Designed to support consistency without guilt.</h2>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <p class="feature-kicker">Lightweight</p>
                    <h2>Quick daily check-ins that never feel like homework.</h2>
                </article>
            </section>

            <section class="details-grid" id="rhythm">
                <article class="detail-card detail-card-large">
                    <p class="section-label">Daily rhythm</p>
                    <h3>Less planning. More returning.</h3>
                    <p>
                        Build a tiny routine you can actually keep. Drift is made for small actions that
                        repeat gently over time, helping momentum grow without adding pressure.
                    </p>
                </article>

                <article class="detail-card">
                    <p class="section-label">A calmer interface</p>
                    <h3>Minimal by design</h3>
                    <p>Clear lists, soft progress, and no noisy productivity mechanics competing for attention.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="detail-card">
                    <p class="section-label">Steady progress</p>
                    <h3>Consistency over perfection</h3>
                    <p>Celebrate showing up often, not doing everything flawlessly every single day.</p>
                </article>
            </section>

            <section class="support-section" id="support">
                <div>
                    <p class="section-label">Supportive by default</p>
                    <h2>A habit tool that feels like a quiet companion.</h2>
                </div>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="button button-primary">Create your first routine</a>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/theme-toggle.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
